<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Memorandum of Understanding</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 0;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #333333;
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            print-color-adjust: exact;
            font-size: 11px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .a4-container {
            width: 210mm;
            min-height: 297mm;
            position: relative;
            background: white;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Top Wave Banner */
        .top-banner {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 60mm;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .wave-svg {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .header-content {
            position: absolute;
            top: 25mm;
            left: 20mm;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .doc-title {
            color: #f37021;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .doc-subtitle {
            color: #f37021;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        /* Content Layer */
        .content-layer {
            flex-grow: 1;
            padding: 10mm 20mm 20mm 20mm;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .section-header {
            color: #f37021;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-transform: capitalize;
        }

        .section-text {
            color: #555555;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .section-text p {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .section-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        .section-list li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            color: #555555;
        }

        .section-list li::before {
            content: "•";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #f37021;
        }

        /* Parties Info */
        .parties-grid {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .party-info {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .underline-field {
            display: inline-block;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #999;
            min-width: 150px;
            margin-left: 5px;
            padding-bottom: 1px;
        }

        /* Signature Area */
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }

        .sig-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .sig-block {
            width: 45%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-end;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .sig-label {
            white-space: nowrap;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .sig-line {
            flex-grow: 1;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #999;
            height: 20px;
        }

        .date-block {
            width: 35%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-end;
            gap: 10px;
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="a4-container">
        <!-- Top Wave Banner -->
        <div class="top-banner">
            <svg class="wave-svg" viewBox="0 0 800 250" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <!-- Bottom wave (lighter) -->
                <path d="M0,0 C200,10 400,150 800,40 L800,0 L0,0 Z" fill="#fff4e6" />
                <!-- Middle wave -->
                <path d="M0,0 C300,50 500,180 800,70 L800,0 L0,0 Z" fill="#ffb380" />
                <!-- Top wave (actual orange) -->
                <path d="M0,0 C350,80 600,160 800,100 L800,0 L0,0 Z" fill="#f37021" />
            </svg>
            <div class="header-content">
                <div class="doc-title">Memorandum of</div>
                <div class="doc-subtitle">Understanding</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content-layer">
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">1. Agreement Overview</div>
                <div class="section-text">
                    <p>This Memorandum of Understanding is entered into by:</p>
                    <div class="parties-grid">
                        <div class="party-info"><strong>First Party</strong> : <span class="underline-field">{{partyName}}</span></div>
                        <div class="party-info"><strong>Second Party</strong> : <span class="underline-field">{{companyName}}</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">2. Background and Purpose</div>
                <div class="section-text">
                    <p>{{#if background}}{{background}}{{else}}The parties wish to enter into this MOU to explore and establish a framework for collaboration in their respective fields of expertise and mutual business objectives.{{/if}}</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">3. Areas of Collaboration</div>
                <ul class="section-list">
                    {{#if collaborationAreas}}
                        {{#each collaborationAreas}}
                            <li>{{this}}</li>
                        {{/each}}
                    {{else}}
                        <li>Joint research and development initiatives.</li>
                        <li>Marketing and promotional activities.</li>
                        <li>Sharing of technical expertise and resources.</li>
                    {{/if}}
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">4. Roles and Responsibilities</div>
                <div class="section-text">
                    <p><strong>Party A</strong> shall be responsible for: {{#if partyARoles}}{{partyARoles}}{{else}}Allocating necessary personnel and providing technical documentation.{{/if}}</p>
                    <p><strong>Party B</strong> shall be responsible for: {{#if partyBRoles}}{{partyBRoles}}{{else}}Providing market insights and facilitating stakeholder engagement.{{/if}}</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">5. Term and Termination</div>
                <div class="section-text">
                    <p>This MOU shall remain in effect until modified or terminated by mutual consent. Either party may terminate this agreement with written notice if objectives are not met.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">6. Confidentiality</div>
                <div class="section-text">
                    <p>Both parties agree to maintain confidentiality of all proprietary and sensitive information exchanged during the term of this Agreement.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            {{#if sections}}
                {{#each sections}}
                    <div class="section">
                        <div class="section-header">{{#if @index}}{{add @index 7}}{{else}}7{{/if}}. {{this.heading}}</div>
                        <div class="section-text">
                            <p>{{this.content}}</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                {{/each}}
            {{/if}}

            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">{{#if sections}}{{add (length sections) 7}}{{else}}7{{/if}}. Acceptance and Signatures</div>
                <div class="section-text">
                    <p>By signing below, both parties agree to the terms outlined in this Memorandum of Understanding.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="signature-section">
                    <div class="sig-row">
                        <div class="sig-block">
                            <span class="sig-label">Party A Signature</span>
                            <div class="sig-line"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="date-block">
                            <span class="sig-label">Date :</span>
                            <div class="sig-line"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sig-row">
                        <div class="sig-block">
                            <span class="sig-label">Party B Signature</span>
                            <div class="sig-line"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="date-block">
                            <span class="sig-label">Date :</span>
                            <div class="sig-line"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
